## 7. Troubleshooting & Common Issues

| Issue | Cause | Solution |
|-------|-------|----------|
| `cannot find symbol` | Class not defined or typo | Check class name matches exactly (case-sensitive) |
| Compilation fails | Missing method implementation | Review required methods in README.md |
| Balance doesn't update | Mutation method not called | Ensure `deposit()`/`withdraw()` are called, not direct manipulation |
| Transaction history empty | `recordTransaction()` not called | Add `recordTransaction()` call after balance update |
| Inheritance not working | `extend` misspelled or wrong parent | Use `extends` keyword with correct parent class name |
| Output not showing | `println()` not invoked | Add `System.out.println()` in Main.main() |

